name: Egg Hunt XR
summary: Egg Hunt XR transforms your world into an egg-hunting paradise! Explore your surroundings, find hidden eggs, and collect them in your bucket before time runs out. Every hunt is different, with eggs appearing in new spots each time you play. With colorful surprises and a festive atmosphere, this short holiday adventure is perfect for all. How many eggs can you gather? Play again and again to beat your best score and discover every hidden...
